#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:234
msgid ""
"Do not forget to change back the alias of the sales team and the catchall "
"value on the mail alias domain, just as they were before this procedure."
msgstr ""
"Muista muuttaa myyntitiimin alias ja catchall-arvo sГӨhkГ¶postialiaksen "
"verkkotunnuksessa takaisin ennalleen, kuten ne olivat ennen tГӨtГӨ menettelyГӨ."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:237
msgid ""
"An alternative to redirections is **forwarding**. With forwarding, **the "
"address forwarding the email will be identified as the sender**, while with "
"redirections, the original sender will always remain."
msgstr ""
"Vaihtoehto uudelleenohjauksille on **edelleenlГӨhetys**. EdelleenlГӨhetyksessГӨ "
"**sГӨhkГ¶postin edelleenlГӨhettГӨvГӨ osoite tunnistetaan lГӨhettГӨjГӨksi**, kun taas "
"uudelleenohjauksissa alkuperГӨinen lГӨhettГӨjГӨ sГӨilyy aina."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:242
msgid ""
"When using email redirection to manage incoming messages, additional "
"configuration may be required to ensure correct behavior."
msgstr ""
"Kun kГӨytГӨt sГӨhkГ¶postin uudelleenohjausta saapuvien viestien hallintaan, "
"lisГӨmГӨГӨrityksiГӨ voidaan tarvita oikean toiminnan varmistamiseksi."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:245
msgid ""
"Some email providers, such as Gmail, require the redirection address to be "
"explicitly confirmed before emails are forwarded, otherwise the redirection "
"may not function."
msgstr ""
"Jotkin sГӨhkГ¶postipalveluntarjoajat, kuten Gmail, vaativat "
"uudelleenohjausosoitteen nimenomaisesti vahvistettavaksi ennen kuin "
"sГӨhkГ¶postiviestejГӨ vГӨlitetГӨГӨn edelleen, muuten uudelleenohjaus ei "
"vГӨlttГӨmГӨttГӨ toimi."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:248
msgid ""
"In addition, when redirection is used instead of an incoming mail server, "
"the alias may appear with the `@yourdb.odoo.com` domain unless *Local-part "
"based incoming detection* is enabled on the corresponding alias. This "
"setting can be found under :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> "
"Aliases`."
msgstr ""
"LisГӨksi, kun kГӨytetГӨГӨn uudelleenohjausta saapuvan postin palvelimen sijasta, "
"alias saattaa nГӨkyГӨ `@yourdb.odoo.com`-verkkotunnuksella, ellei vastaavalle "
"aliakselle ole otettu kГӨyttГ¶Г¶n *paikalliseen osaan perustuvaa saapuvan "
"postin tunnistusta*. TГӨmГӨ asetus lГ¶ytyy kohdasta :menuselection:`Asetukset --"
"> Tekniset --> Aliakset`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:256
msgid "Incoming mail servers"
msgstr "Saapuvan postin palvelimet"

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:258
msgid ""
"As mentioned earlier, using redirections is the recommended method to "
"receive emails in Odoo. However, it is also possible to set up incoming mail "
"servers. Using this method means creating an incoming email server for each "
"mailbox on your server, catchall, bounce, and every alias of the database, "
"in order to fetch all incoming emails."
msgstr ""
"Kuten aiemmin mainittiin, uudelleenohjausten kГӨyttГ¶ on suositeltu tapa "
"vastaanottaa sГӨhkГ¶posteja Odoon. On kuitenkin myГ¶s mahdollista mГӨГӨrittГӨГӨ "
"saapuvan postin palvelimia. TГӨmГӨn menetelmГӨn kГӨyttГ¶ tarkoittaa saapuvan "
"sГӨhkГ¶postin palvelimen luomista jokaiselle palvelimesi postilaatikolle, "
"catchallille, bouncelle ja tietokannan jokaiselle aliakselle, jotta kaikki "
"saapuvat sГӨhkГ¶postit haetaan."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:264
msgid ""
"Odoo's *Incoming Mail Servers* feature is designed for shared inboxes (e.g., "
"`sales@yourcompany.com` or `support@yourcompany.com`) to route messages to "
"team pipelines, tickets, or documents."
msgstr ""
"Odoon *Saapuvien sГӨhkГ¶postipalvelimien* ominaisuus on suunniteltu jaettuihin "
"postilaatikoihin (esim. `sales@yourcompany.com` tai "
"`support@yourcompany.com`) ohjaamaan viestejГӨ tiimien putkiin, tiketteihin "
"tai asiakirjoihin."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:268
msgid ""
"Using personal email addresses (e.g., `mitchell.admin@yourcompany.com`) as "
"incoming mail servers is **not** recommended. Doing so can lead to increased "
"security risks, unintended message routing, privacy issues, and difficulties "
"syncing replies correctly."
msgstr ""
"HenkilГ¶kohtaisten sГӨhkГ¶postiosoitteiden (esim. "
"`mitchell.admin@yourcompany.com`) kГӨyttГӨminen saapuvina "
"sГӨhkГ¶postipalvelimina **ei** ole suositeltavaa. TГӨmГӨ voi johtaa "
"lisГӨГӨntyneisiin tietoturvariskeihin, tahattomaan viestien reititykseen, "
"yksityisyysongelmiin ja vaikeuksiin synkronoida vastauksia oikein."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:272
msgid ""
"Incoming mail servers are created by going to :menuselection:`Settings --> "
"Technical --> Emails: Incoming Mail Servers`."
msgstr ""
"Saapuvat sГӨhkГ¶postipalvelimet luodaan siirtymГӨllГӨ "
"kohtaan :menuselection:`Asetukset --> Tekniset --> SГӨhkГ¶postit: Saapuvat "
"sГӨhkГ¶postipalvelimet`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:276
msgid ""
"We recommend using the IMAP protocol over the POP protocol, as IMAP fetches "
"all unread emails, while POP fetches all the emails' history and then tags "
"them as deleted in your mailbox."
msgstr ""
"Suosittelemme IMAP-protokollan kГӨyttГӨmistГӨ POP-protokollan sijaan, sillГӨ "
"IMAP hakee kaikki lukemattomat sГӨhkГ¶postit, kun taas POP hakee kaiken "
"sГӨhkГ¶postihistorian ja merkitsee viestit sen jГӨlkeen poistetuiksi "
"postilaatikossasi."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:280
msgid ""
"It is also possible to connect a mailbox through :doc:`Gmail with Google "
"OAuth <google_oauth>` or :doc:`Outlook with Microsoft Azure OAuth "
"<azure_oauth>`."
msgstr ""
"On myГ¶s mahdollista yhdistГӨГӨ postilaatikko :doc:`Gmailin kautta Google "
"OAuthilla <google_oauth>` tai :doc:`Outlookin kautta Microsoft Azure "
"OAuthilla <azure_oauth>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:283
msgid ""
"Regardless of the protocol chosen, emails are fetched using the *Mail: "
"Fetchmail Service* scheduled action."
msgstr ""
"KГӨytetystГӨ protokollasta riippumatta sГӨhkГ¶postit haetaan kГӨyttГӨen "
"*SГӨhkГ¶posti: Fetchmail-palvelu* -ajastettua toimintoa."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:286
msgid ""
"Additionally, using an incoming mail server in Odoo gives the opportunity to "
"create new records in a specified model. Each incoming mail server can "
"create records in a different model."
msgstr ""
"LisГӨksi saapuvan sГӨhkГ¶postipalvelimen kГӨyttГ¶ Odoossa antaa mahdollisuuden "
"luoda uusia tietueita mГӨГӨritettyyn malliin. Jokainen saapuva "
"sГӨhkГ¶postipalvelin voi luoda tietueita eri malliin."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:290
msgid ""
"Emails received on `task@company-name.com` are fetched by the Odoo database. "
"All fetched emails will create a new project task in the database."
msgstr ""
"Osoitteeseen `task@company-name.com` saapuvat sГӨhkГ¶postit haetaan Odoo-"
"tietokantaan. Kaikki haetut sГӨhkГ¶postit luovat uuden projektitehtГӨvГӨn "
"tietokantaan."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:299
msgid "MX record"
msgstr "MX-tietue"

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:301
msgid ""
"A third option is to create a MX record in your DNS zone which specifies the "
"mail server managing emails sent to your domain. **Advanced technical "
"knowledge is required.**"
msgstr ""
"Kolmas vaihtoehto on luoda MX-tietue DNS-vyГ¶hykkeeseen, joka mГӨГӨrittГӨГӨ "
"verkkotunnukseesi lГӨhetettyjГӨ sГӨhkГ¶posteja hallinnoivan "
"sГӨhkГ¶postipalvelimen. **Vaatii edistynyttГӨ teknistГӨ osaamista.**"

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:305
msgid ""
"This configuration only works with a subdomain on the Odoo Online or Odoo.sh "
"infrastructure (e.g., `@mail.mydomain.com`). Point the MX record from the "
"custom subdomain to the Odoo subdomain of your database, e.g., from "
"`mail.mydomain.com` to `dbname.odoo.com`."
msgstr ""
"TГӨmГӨ kokoonpano toimii vain aliverkkotunnuksella Odoo Online- tai Odoo.sh-"
"infrastruktuurissa (esim. `@mail.mydomain.com`). Ohjaa MX-tietue "
"mukautetusta aliverkkotunnuksesta tietokantasi Odoo-aliverkkotunnukseen, "
"esim. osoitteesta `mail.mydomain.com` osoitteeseen `dbname.odoo.com`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:309
msgid "Below are presented some specifications depending on the hosting type:"
msgstr "Alla esitetГӨГӨn joitakin mГӨГӨrityksiГӨ riippuen hosting-tyypistГӨ:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:313
#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/faq.rst:296
