msgstr "Odoo Online"

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:315
msgid ""
"The custom subdomain must be added to your :doc:`Odoo Portal <../../websites/"
"website/configuration/domain_names>`."
msgstr ""
"Mukautettu aliverkkotunnus on lisГӨttГӨvГӨ :doc:`Odoo-portaaliin <../../"
