#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:318
#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/faq.rst:301
msgid "Odoo.sh"
msgstr "Odoo.sh"

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:320
msgid ""
"The custom subdomain must be added to the :doc:`settings of the project "
"<../../../administration/odoo_sh/getting_started/settings>`:"
msgstr ""
"Mukautettu aliverkkotunnus on lisГӨttГӨvГӨ :doc:`projektin asetuksiin <../../../"
"administration/odoo_sh/getting_started/settings>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:0
msgid "Adding a custom subdomain for mail to Odoo.sh project settings."
msgstr ""
"Mukautetun sГӨhkГ¶postin aliverkkotunnuksen lisГӨГӨminen Odoo.sh-projektin "
"asetuksiin."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:329
msgid "Infinite email loops"
msgstr "Г„ГӨrettГ¶mГӨt sГӨhkГ¶postisilmukat"

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:331
msgid ""
"In some cases, infinite mailing loops can be created. Odoo provides some "
"protection against such loops, ensuring the same sender cannot send too many "
"emails **that would create records** to an alias in a specific time span."
msgstr ""
"Joissakin tapauksissa voi syntyГӨ ГӨГӨrettГ¶miГӨ sГӨhkГ¶postisilmukoita. Odoo "
"tarjoaa suojaa tГӨllaisia silmukoita vastaan varmistaen, ettГӨ sama lГӨhettГӨjГӨ "
"ei voi lГӨhettГӨГӨ liian montaa sГӨhkГ¶postia **jotka luovat tietueita** "
"aliakselle tietyssГӨ ajanjaksossa."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:335
msgid ""
"By default, an email address can send up to 20 emails in 120 minutes. If "
"more emails are sent, they are blocked and the sender receives the following "
"message:"
msgstr ""
"Oletusarvoisesti sГӨhkГ¶postiosoite voi lГӨhettГӨГӨ enintГӨГӨn 20 sГӨhkГ¶postia 120 "
"minuutissa. Jos sГӨhkГ¶posteja lГӨhetetГӨГӨn enemmГӨn, ne estetГӨГӨn ja lГӨhettГӨjГӨ "
"saa seuraavan viestin:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:None
msgid "Bounce email received after attempting contact too many times an alias."
msgstr ""
"Palautunut sГӨhkГ¶posti, joka vastaanotettiin yritettГӨessГӨ ottaa yhteyttГӨ "
"aliakseen liian monta kertaa."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:341
msgid ""
"To change the default behavior, enable :ref:`developer-mode`, then go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> Parameters: System Parameters` "
"to add two parameters."
msgstr ""
"OletuskГӨyttГӨytymisen muuttamiseksi ota kГӨyttГ¶Г¶n :ref:`developer-mode`, "
"siirry sitten kohtaan :menuselection:`Asetukset --> Tekniset --> Parametrit: "
"JГӨrjestelmГӨparametrit` lisГӨtГӨksesi kaksi parametria."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:344
msgid ""
"For the first parameter, enter `mail.gateway.loop.minutes` as "
"the :guilabel:`Key` and choose a number of minutes as the :guilabel:`Value` "
"(`120` is the default behavior)."
msgstr ""
"EnsimmГӨiseksi parametriksi syГ¶tГӨ "
"`mail.gateway.loop.minutes` :guilabel:`Avaimeksi` ja valitse "
"minuuttimГӨГӨrГӨksi :guilabel:`Arvo` (`120` on oletuskГӨyttГӨytyminen)."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:346
msgid ""
"For the second parameter, enter `mail.gateway.loop.threshold` as "
"the :guilabel:`Key` and choose a number of emails as the :guilabel:`Value` "
"(`20` is the default behavior)."
msgstr ""
"Toiseksi parametriksi syГ¶tГӨ "
"`mail.gateway.loop.threshold` :guilabel:`Avaimeksi` ja valitse sГӨhkГ¶postien "
"lukumГӨГӨrГӨksi :guilabel:`Arvo` (`20` on oletuskГӨyttГӨytyminen)."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:350
msgid "Allow alias domain system parameter"
msgstr "AliasverkkotunnusjГӨrjestelmГӨn parametrin salliminen"

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:352
msgid ""
"Incoming aliases are set in the Odoo database to create records by receiving "
"incoming emails. To view aliases set in the Odoo database, first activate "
"the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`. Then, go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical --> Aliases`."
msgstr ""
"Saapuvat aliakset asetetaan Odoo-tietokannassa luomaan tietueita "
"vastaanottamalla saapuvia sГӨhkГ¶posteja. NГӨhdГӨksesi Odoo-tietokannassa "
"asetetut aliakset, aktivoi ensin :ref:`kehittГӨjГӨtila <developer-mode>`. "
"Siirry sitten kohtaan :menuselection:`Asetukset-sovellus --> Tekniset --> "
"Aliakset`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:356
msgid ""
"The following system parameter, `mail.catchall.domain.allowed`, set with "
"allowed alias domain values, separated by commas, filters out correctly "
"addressed emails to aliases. Setting the domains for which the alias can "
"create a ticket, lead, opportunity, etc., eliminates false positives where "
"email addresses with only the prefix alias, not the domain, are present."
msgstr ""
"Seuraava jГӨrjestelmГӨparametri, `mail.catchall.domain.allowed`, joka on "
"asetettu sallituilla aliasverkkotunnusarvoilla pilkuilla erotettuna, "
"suodattaa oikein osoitetut sГӨhkГ¶postit aliaksille. Verkkotunnusten "
"asettaminen, joille alias voi luoda tikettejГӨ, liidit, mahdollisuuksia jne., "
"eliminoi vГӨГӨrГӨt positiiviset tulokset, joissa on vain aliaksen etuliite, ei "
"verkkotunnusta."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:361
msgid ""
"In some instances, matches have been made in the Odoo database when an email "
"is received with the same alias prefix and a different domain on the "
"incoming email address. This is true in the sender, recipient, and :abbr:`CC "
"(Carbon Copy)` email addresses of an incoming email."
msgstr ""
"Joissakin tapauksissa Odoo-tietokannassa on tehty osumia, kun vastaanotetaan "
"sГӨhkГ¶posti, jossa on sama aliaksen etuliite ja eri verkkotunnus saapuvassa "
"sГӨhkГ¶postiosoitteessa. TГӨmГӨ pГӨtee lГӨhettГӨjГӨГӨn, vastaanottajaan ja :abbr:`CC "
"(hiilikopio)` -sГӨhkГ¶postiosoitteisiin saapuvassa sГӨhkГ¶postissa."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:366
msgid ""
"When Odoo receives emails with the `commercial` prefix alias in the sender, "
"recipient, or :abbr:`CC (Carbon Copy)` email addresses (e.g. "
"commercial\\@example.com), the database falsely treats the email as the full "
"`commercial` alias, with a different domain, and therefore, creates a ticket/"
"lead/opportunity/etc."
msgstr ""
"Kun Odoo vastaanottaa sГӨhkГ¶posteja, joissa on `commercial`-etuliitealias "
"lГӨhettГӨjГӨssГӨ, vastaanottajassa tai :abbr:`CC (hiilikopio)` "
"-sГӨhkГ¶postiosoitteissa (esim. commercial\\@example.com), tietokanta "
"kГӨsittelee virheellisesti sГӨhkГ¶postin tГӨytenГӨ `commercial`-aliaksena, jossa "
"on eri verkkotunnus, ja luo siksi tiketin/liidin/mahdollisuuden/jne."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:371
msgid ""
"To add the `mail.catchall.domain.allowed` system parameter, first, activate "
"the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`. Then, go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical --> System Parameters`. "
"Click :guilabel:`New`. Then, type in `mail.catchall.domain.allowed` for "
"the :guilabel:`Key` field."
msgstr ""
"LisГӨtГӨksesi `mail.catchall.domain.allowed` -jГӨrjestelmГӨparametrin, aktivoi "
"ensin :ref:`kehittГӨjГӨtila <developer-mode>`. Siirry sitten "
"kohtaan :menuselection:`Asetukset-sovellus --> Tekniset --> "
"JГӨrjestelmГӨparametrit`. Napsauta :guilabel:`Uusi`. Kirjoita sitten "
"`mail.catchall.domain.allowed` :guilabel:`Avain`-kenttГӨГӨn."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:375
msgid ""
"Next, for the :guilabel:`Value` field, add the domains separated by commas. "
"Manually :icon:`fa-cloud-upload` :guilabel:`(Save)`, and the system "
"parameter takes immediate effect."
msgstr ""
"Seuraavaksi lisГӨГӨ :guilabel:`Arvo`-kenttГӨГӨn verkkotunnukset pilkuilla "
"erotettuna. Tallenna manuaalisesti :icon:`fa-cloud-"
"upload` :guilabel:`(Tallenna)`, ja jГӨrjestelmГӨparametri tulee voimaan "
"vГӨlittГ¶mГӨsti."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:None
msgid "mail.catchall.domain.allowed system parameter set."
msgstr "mail.catchall.domain.allowed -jГӨrjestelmГӨparametri asetettu."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:382
msgid "Local-part based incoming detection"
msgstr "Paikallisiin osiin perustuva saapuvien lГӨhetysten havaitseminen"

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_inbound.rst:384
msgid ""
"When creating a new alias, there is an option to enable :guilabel:`Local-"
"part based incoming detection`. If enabled, Odoo only requires the local-"
"part to match for routing an incoming email. If this feature is turned off, "
"Odoo requires the whole email address to match for routing an incoming email."
msgstr ""
"Uutta aliasta luotaessa on mahdollista ottaa "
"kГӨyttГ¶Г¶n :guilabel:`Paikallisosaan perustuva saapuvan tunnistus`. Jos tГӨmГӨ "
"on kГӨytГ¶ssГӨ, Odoo vaatii vain paikallisosan tГӨsmГӨГӨmisen saapuvan sГӨhkГ¶postin "
"reitityksessГӨ. Jos tГӨmГӨ ominaisuus on pois pГӨГӨltГӨ, Odoo vaatii koko "
"sГӨhkГ¶postiosoitteen tГӨsmГӨГӨmisen saapuvan sГӨhkГ¶postin reitityksessГӨ."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_outbound.rst:3
msgid "Manage outbound messages"
msgstr "LГӨhtevien viestien hallinta"

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_outbound.rst:8
msgid "Sending emails with Odoo's default configuration"
msgstr "SГӨhkГ¶postien lГӨhettГӨminen Odoon oletuskonfiguraatiolla"

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_outbound.rst:10
msgid ""
"On **Odoo Online** and **Odoo.sh**, sending and receiving emails works out "
"of the box. No configuration is required."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo Onlinessa** ja **Odoo.sh:ssa** sГӨhkГ¶postien lГӨhettГӨminen ja "
"vastaanottaminen toimii heti. Konfigurointia ei tarvita."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_outbound.rst:13
msgid ""
"When a database is created, the subdomain `company-name.odoo.com` is used to "
"send and receive emails. The deliverability is optimized for this subdomain "
"as it uses OdooвҖҷs DNS configuration."
msgstr ""
"Kun tietokanta luodaan, aliverkkotunnusta `company-name.odoo.com` kГӨytetГӨГӨn "
"sГӨhkГ¶postien lГӨhettГӨmiseen ja vastaanottamiseen. Toimitettavuus on optimoitu "
"tГӨlle aliverkkotunnukselle, koska se kГӨyttГӨГӨ Odoon DNS-konfiguraatiota."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_outbound.rst:17
msgid ""
"If the database subdomain is `company-name.odoo.com` and all mailing "
"configurations are the default ones, all emails will be sent from "
"`notifications@company-name.odoo.com`."
msgstr ""
"Jos tietokannan aliverkkotunnus on `company-name.odoo.com` ja kaikki "
"sГӨhkГ¶postikonfiguraatiot ovat oletusarvoisia, kaikki sГӨhkГ¶postit lГӨhetetГӨГӨn "
"osoitteesta `notifications@company-name.odoo.com`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/email_servers_outbound.rst:22
msgid ""
"This configuration is handled by the system parameter "
"`mail.default.from_filter`. In case where the sender's domain do not match "
"the value of this parameter, the notification address is used instead. "
"Multiple values can be defined in this system parameter: comma-separated, "
"domains or full email addresses are all allowed. Once an :ref:`outgoing mail "
"server is configured <email-outbound-different-servers-personalized>`, the "
"system parameter is no longer considered and the value used is "
"the :ref:`FROM filtering <email-outbound-different-servers-personalized-from-"
"filtering>` of the mail server."
msgstr ""
"TГӨtГӨ konfiguraatiota hallitaan jГӨrjestelmГӨparametrilla "
"`mail.default.from_filter`. SiinГӨ tapauksessa, ettГӨ lГӨhettГӨjГӨn verkkotunnus "
"ei tГӨsmГӨГӨ tГӨmГӨn parametrin arvoon, kГӨytetГӨГӨn sen sijaan ilmoitusosoitetta. "
