"Napsauta sen jГӨlkeen :guilabel:`Create Project`, joka "
"sijaitsee :guilabel:`OAuth consent screen` -sivun oikeassa reunassa. Jos "
"tГӨlle tilille on jo luotu projekti, :guilabel:`New Project` -vaihtoehto "
"sijaitsee oikeassa ylГӨkulmassa :guilabel:`Select a project` -pudotusvalikon "
"alla."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/google_oauth.rst:33
msgid ""
"On the :menuselection:`New Project` screen, rename the :guilabel:`Project "
"name` to `Odoo` and browse for the :guilabel:`Location`. Set "
"the :guilabel:`Location` as the *Google Workspace organization*. If you are "
"using a personal Gmail account, then leave the :guilabel:`Location` "
"as :guilabel:`No Organization`."
msgstr ""
":menuselection:`New Project` -nГӨytГ¶llГӨ nimeГӨ :guilabel:`Project name` "
"uudelleen muotoon `Odoo` ja selaa :guilabel:`Location`. "
"Aseta :guilabel:`Sijainti` *Google Workspace -organisaatioksi*. Jos kГӨytГӨt "
"henkilГ¶kohtaista Gmail-tiliГӨ, jГӨtГӨ :guilabel:`Sijainti` arvoon :guilabel:`No "
"Organization`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/google_oauth.rst:None
