"settings are needed to configure Mailjet in Odoo, which is covered in "
"the :ref:`last section <maintain/mailjet-api/odoo-setup>`."
msgstr ""
"Kopioi sitten :abbr:`SMTP-mГӨГӨritysasetukset (Simple Mail Transfer Protocol)` "
