"`Mailjet: How can I configure my SMTP parameters? <https://"
"documentation.mailjet.com/hc/articles/360043229473>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Mailjet: How can I configure my SMTP parameters? <https://"
"documentation.mailjet.com/hc/articles/360043229473>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication/mailjet_api.rst:35
