"--> Laitteet` ja napsauta viivakoodinlukijan korttia. Valitse sitten oikea "
"kieli :guilabel:`NГӨppГӨimistГ¶asettelu` -kentГӨstГӨ."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:475
#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/devices/printer.rst:505
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Keyboard Layout` is language-specific, with available options "
